'''სერბია''' (Србија / ''Srbija'') is a [[landlocked]] country in central and southeastern [[Europe]]. The capital is [[Belgrade]]. Serbia borders [[Hungary]] to the north; [[Romania]] and [[Bulgaria]] to the east; the [[Republic of Macedonia]] and [[Albania]] to the south; and [[Montenegro]], [[Croatia]], and [[Bosnia-Herzegovina]] to the west.
